quran[3]{c,v,t}:
  102,0,shuru allah ka naam le kar jo bara meharban nihayat reham wala hai
  102,1,( logo ) tum ko ( maal ki ) bohat si talab ne ghaafil kar diya
  102,2,yahan taq ke tum ne qabrain ja dekhen
  102,3,dekho tumhe anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga
  102,4,phir dekho tumhe anqareeb maloom ho jaye ga
  102,5,dekho agar tum jantay ( yani ) ilm al-yaqeen ( rakhtay to ghaflat nah karte )
  102,6,tum zaroor dozakh ko dekho ge
  102,7,phir is ko ( aisa ) dekho ge ( ke ) ain al-yaqeen ( aa jaye ga )
  102,8,phir is roz tum se ( shukar ) Nemat ke baray mein prssh ho gi
